
"No need to thank me. I'm your husband." I said kissing her forehead and we got into bed.
"But still thank you. I was being mean earlier." She said.
"not really babe. It's cool we all have our days." I shrugged and she nodded before kissing me.
Today was a good day, it was one of my few off days and I got to spend it being inside the house with my family.I most importantly, spent time with my kids and I got to give my wife a break.
